      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Urgent: Addressing Punctuality Concerns\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to address a matter that has come to our attention regarding your punctuality. As you may be aware, punctuality is a critical component of our team's success. It is essential for maintaining a smooth workflow and ensuring that all team members can collaborate effectively.\n\nOver the past two weeks, we have noticed that you have been arriving approximately 15 minutes late to your shifts. While we understand that unforeseen circumstances can sometimes cause delays, it is important to remember that consistent tardiness can disrupt the team's schedule and negatively impact our collective productivity.\n\nWe value your contributions to our team and would like to remind you that punctuality is a key expectation for all employees. We trust that you understand the importance of arriving on time and will make every effort to adhere to the scheduled start times.\n\nPlease take this as a formal warning. If this behavior continues, we may need to consider further disciplinary action. We hope that you will take this matter seriously and make the necessary adjustments to ensure that you arrive on time for all future shifts.\n\nThank you for your attention to this matter. We appreciate your cooperation and look forward to your",
